==English==
=== Etymology ===
From French ''[[résumé#French|résumé]]'', noun use of the past participle of ''[[résumer#French|résumer]]'', to summarize, from {{L.}} ''[[resumere]]'', to take back; compare '''[[resume]]'''

====Alternative spellings====
*[[resume]], [[resumé]]

